Class CONSTANTS

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usfirst.frc.team2791.robot.util.CONSTANTS

  • public class CONSTANTS
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds all important constants that are used in the code. Our main utility in here is for PID tuning constants which we have found experimentally.
